<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Share Story</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #55dd55;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            animation: slideInFromTop 1s ease-in-out;
            font-size: 3em;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        .button-group button {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            color: #010101;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: 2px solid #a4a4a4;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .button-group button:hover {
            background-color: #4ebd4e;
            color: #fff;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        footer b {
            color: #55dd55;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .container {
            width: 70%;
            margin: 50px 15%;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
            display: flex;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container p {
            height: 300px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            display: flex;
        }

        .container img {
            max-width: 80%;
            height: auto;
            max-height: 300px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            transform: scale(0.95);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .container img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Keyframe Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInFromTop {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(-50px);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        hr {
            width: 80%;
            height: 2px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            background-color: #aeaeae;
            border: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <h1>Share Story</h1>
    <div class="button-group">
        <button onclick="window.location.href='explore'">Explore</button>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='add_story'">Add Your Story</button>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <p>"Share-Story" is an innovative platform that revolutionizes the way people connect and share their stories with the world. Express yourself and create meaningful connections through storytelling.</p>
        <img src="img1.jpg" alt="Illustration of a storytelling app in action">
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="container">
        <img src="img2.jpg" alt="Thematic community collaboration visual">
        <p>Join thematic communities to engage with like-minded storytellers, collaborate on creative projects, and provide feedback to others.</p>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="container">
        <p>Participate in "Story Challenges" to unleash your creativity and win global recognition for your storytelling skills.</p>
        <img src="img3.jpg" alt="A creative challenge visual with users competing">
    </div>
    <div class="button-group">
        <button onclick="window.location.href='explore'">Explore</button>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='add_story'">Add Your Story</button>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p><b>Share Story</b> &copy; 2023-2024. <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>